race.comment: Super competitive heat of the Mile series. HIDDEN BOUNTY (9) is a progressive type in sparkling form and can measure up again. Went straight from a maiden win to a BM68 success and gets same rider and the inside draw. Worth following up. OXFORD BLUE (1) is back from a spell and will be primed to run well. Placed at Sandown when last resuming and presents on the back of a jump-out win. Looks well placed here with the claim. WEST CLIFF (3) turned in a much better run second-up to place and is a third-up winner. Has the low draw and should be ready to fire. IMPOSING SUSPECT (2) turned in an eye-catching run in town fresh when fourth and beaten a couple of lengths. Has a super consistent second-up record so must be included.
